      <akn:section eId="sec_44_104_02">
        <akn:num>44-104.02</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Civil Penalties.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-104_02_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Mayor may impose one or more of the civil penalties authorized under ยง 44-509 against persons who:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-104_02_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Notwithstanding any other provision of law, penalties authorized under ยง 44-509 shall not be imposed by the Mayor unless a violation, cited during an inspection:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-104_02_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If during a follow-up inspection the Mayor determines that violations within the control of the facility which were cited in an immediately prior inspection have not been corrected or have recurred, the Mayor may impose penalties authorized under ยง 44-509</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-104_02_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Appeals under this section may be taken pursuant to subchapter XII of this chapter.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
